body_html: I met the same problem today and had fixed it. You just need to download the newest tensorflow source code from github and copy ./tensorflow/tensorboard to the tensorboard you installed(for you it's /usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/tensorflow/tensorboard/)
